NAME Lock and Leave
DESCRIPTION Run recon then lock the workstation
CATEGORY post
PLATFORMS WIN,MAC,LINUX
PLATFORM ALL
DELAY 500
PRINT Gathering info...
OPEN_TERMINAL
STRINGLN whoami
DELAY 500
STRINGLN hostname
DELAY 500
PRINT Locking workstation...
LED_COLOR RED
DELAY 1000
LOCK_SCREEN
LED_COLOR GREEN
PRINT Target locked.
